 Lady Gaga 暗示她下一张专辑的主打单曲将于十月推出https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-hints-lead-single-from-next-album-arriving-october-3790256?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lady-gaga-hints-lead-下一张专辑的单曲将于 10 月抵达Adam EnglandTue, 03 Sep 2024 20:07:28 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3790256 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="嘎嘎小姐" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首单曲将是她自上个月与布鲁诺·马尔斯合作《Die With A Smile》以来的第一首新音乐</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-hints-lead-single-from-next-album-arriving-october-3790256">Lady Gaga 的帖子暗示她下一张专辑的主打单曲将于 10 月发布，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="嘎嘎小姐" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Lady-Gaga-album-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Mother Monster 的新音乐即将推出吗？ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a>在社交媒体帖子中暗示将于 10 月推出新专辑和单曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">Lady Gaga – 《Chromatica》评论：来自她自己世界中偶像的纯粹流行庆典</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位歌手的真名是史蒂芬妮·杰尔马诺塔(Stefani Germanotta)，自上周末以来一直在威尼斯参加《小丑：双人舞曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/joker-folie-a-deux"><em>》(Joker: Folie à Deux)</em></a>的首映式，并在今天（9 月 3 日）发布了一张她一周前的日程安排照片。</p><p>在此之下，有几个十月日期，其中一个写着“XX十月：LG7第一首单曲”，暗示她将分享她尚未公布的第七张录音室专辑中的主打单曲。该单曲将是她自上个月与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruno-mars">Bruno Mars</a>惊喜合作的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-and-bruno-mars-70s-country-themed-die-with-a-smile-music-video-3784255">Die With A Smile</a> 》以来的首张新作品，该专辑将是她自 2020 年的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/lady-gaga-chromatica-album-review-2677590">Chromatica</a> 》以来的首张个人 LP。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lady-gaga-confirms-still-in-studio-cant-wait-hear-what-im-working-on-3776307">今年以来，Gaga 一直在工作室里调侃她的帖子</a>，但现阶段人们对这张专辑知之甚少。然而，七月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-mon-truc-en-plumes-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778447">，在巴黎奥运会开幕式上表演</a>后不久，她确实在巴黎街头为歌迷<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-play-fans-in-paris-snippets-from-upcoming-album-lg7-3778678">演奏了专辑中的几个片段</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_dmIltvMaH/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex